            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Dominos 0.6.0</h2>
<ul>
  <li><b>Bring your own everything:</b> the app no longer carries any preset account, tokens, store, or address. On first launch you pick a carryout store by ZIP, and signing in uses your own Domino's account for points, saved cards, and addresses.</li>
  <li><b>Store picker:</b> a new "Choose Store" button finds carryout stores near a ZIP code.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
